setup.init: sudo apt -y update; sudo apt -y upgrade ; sudo apt install wget; cd ~; curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_14.x -o nodesource_setup.sh; sudo bash nodesource_setup.sh; sudo apt install nodejs -y; sudo apt install git -y; sudo apt install python-pip -y;
setup.download_agent: cd /; mkdir canavarl7; cd canavarl7; wget $AGENTLINK;
setup.download_modules: npm install express fs axios events moment delay quick.db child_process
setup.service_setup: cd /lib/systemd/system/; wget $SERVICELINK -O $SERVICENAME; systemctl daemon-reload; systemctl start $SERVICENAME; systemctl enable $SERVICENAME;
